These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, journalist
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, russian
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter
1. the journalist is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the engineer is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | sprite    |
| Job           | journalist | engineer |
| Nationality   | turkish       | russian  |
| Transport     | motorbike      | helicopter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: radish, apple
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, funk
2 different pets are kept: dog, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | apple | radish |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | funk         |
| Pet           | snake     | dog         |
| Transport     | ship    | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, designer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, jazz
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, boat
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the police-officer##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | skydiving          | magic-tricks |
| Job           | designer | police-officer     |
| Music-Genre   | indie            | jazz         |
| Transport     | boat         | car   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, drama
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, techno
2 different pets are kept: cat, lizard
1. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama    | sports |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | techno |
| Pet           | cat | lizard    |

