.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person eating nectarine is the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of trance is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | 7up     | cola |
| Food          | kiwi   | nectarine |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | trance     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter     |

 